  <name>Plexus Summit Component</name>
  <currentVersion>1.0-beta-3</currentVersion>

  <shortDescription>A servlet based framework.</shortDescription>

  <description>
    Summit is a servlet based framework that allows experienced 
    Java developers to quickly build secure web applications. Parts 
    of Summit can also be used independently of the web portion of 
    Summit as well. In other words, we strive to make portions of 
    Summit easily available for use in other applications.
  </description>
  
